snippet.title: SEAL Team Six: Memoirs of an Elite Navy SEAL Sniper
snippet.description: Eventually, of the 18 snipers in SEAL Team Six, Wasdin became the best—which meant one of the best snipers on the planet. Less than half a year after sniper school, he was fighting for his life.

snippet.description: Mark Owen's name and the names of the other SEALs mentioned in this book have been changed for their security. Kevin Maurer has covered special-operations forces for nine years.

snippet.description: The Inside Story of America's Ultimate Warriors When Osama bin Laden was assassinated, the entire world was fascinated by the men who had completed the seemingly impossible mission that had dogged the U.S. government for over a decade.

snippet.title: Fearless: The Undaunted Courage and Ultimate Sacrifice of ...
snippet.description: Fearless is the story of a man of extremes, whose courage and determination was fueled by faith, family, and the love of a woman.

snippet.title: I Am a SEAL Team Six Warrior: Memoirs of an American Soldier
snippet.description: The Battle of Mogadishu, as it become known, left 18 American soldiers dead and 73 wounded. This is Howard Wasdin's story of overcoming numerous obstacles to become an elite American warrior.

snippet.title: SEAL Team Six: Hunt the Scorpion
snippet.description: Don Mann was on active duty with SEAL team six until 1998. SEAL Team Six: Hunt the Scorpion combines his real-life insight with pulse-pounding action and non-stop thrills.

snippet.title: Hunt the Wolf: A SEAL Team Six Novel
snippet.description: HUNT THE WOLF is an adrenaline-packed novel sure to appeal to fans of Vince Flynn and Brad Thor, featuring the world's most elite soldiers and based on the experiences of renowned SEAL Team 6 commando Don Mann.

Impossible Odds: The Kidnapping of Jessica Buchanan and ...
snippet.description: Both a testament to two people’s courage and a nail-biting look at a life-or-death struggle, this is a harrowing and deeply personal story about their triumph over impossible odds.

snippet.title: SEAL Team Six Outcasts
snippet.description: Bitter Ash, a special operations unit, is secretly deployed into enemy territory to eliminate the potential successors to Osama bin Laden's leadership in al Qaeda, but discover a larger plot that puts the United States in jeopardy.
